value.name: Cheektowaga officers, good Samaritans honored for saving woman trapped under car
value.description: Seven officers from the Cheektowaga Police Department and two good samaritans were honored on Monday for saving a pedestrian who became pinned under a car after she was hit. Police say on May 5, a woman in her 60s was hit by a vehicle in a parking lot near Walden Avenue and was dragged a short distance before becoming trapped under it.
